He picks up his laptop and gets obsessed with learning the ins and outs of trading. At first, it was nothing serious.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 13, 2021 tagging @highstrike. May be an image of text that says 'HighStrike @highstrike I would make a few bucks here and there but I never took it too seriously... Until I realized hated working a 9-5 and wanted to live life on my own terms. So I made it a goal to have trading replace my 9-5 income.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 13, 2021 tagging @highstrike. May be an image of text that says 'HighStrike @highstrike It wasn't all sunshine and roses either took some losses on the way, almost daily. But knew that losses were a part of the game, ano the key to winning it was having my wins outweigh my losses.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 13, 2021 tagging @highstrike. May be an image of text that says 'HighStrike @highstrike After 18 months of trading, I finally quit my 9-5 job as an engineer to become a trader. When quit, I was making $5k/m from my job and $10k/m from trading. Now, here's what process... learned in the the'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 13, 2021 tagging @highstrike. That, and the help of starting my own business, is what helped me make my first $1,000,000.'.

Most people: -Don't sleep well -Don't have a routine -Don't learn about themselves You need to: -Build discipline -Create routines -Lean new information'.
